Game features:
	indicate who is drawing
	indicate who is next to draw
	chatbox checks for correct answers in chat input
	when a user correctly guesses, their chat is hidden to users who have not guessed
	user list ordered by draw order
	number next to user's name in list to indicate their place according to score
	timer for each draw
	word displayed at top with blank space based on number of letters
	word at top fills in letters as time passes in round

Server features:
	database!
  
Database features:
	list of words for game
	users
